N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 163.3 - Permit number

State Regulations
A permit number for each product so assigned by the
commissioner to a registered applicant shall, unless temporarily waived by the
commissioner, appear in a place provided upon the trademark label to be used by
said applicant, and such permit number shall be used only by said registered
applicant. Notes
